# Ticket Completion

Follow `backend_doc/templates/backend_ticket_template.md`.

Before marking done, fill the completion manifest:

- Contracts changed (OpenAPI/AsyncAPI paths, error codes, permissions)
- Migration files added
- Tests run with command output (`pnpm verify`, focused tests)
- Security notes (tenant isolation, permission negatives)
- Observability (logs, traces, metrics added)
- Rollback plan
- Unresolved ADR/open questions

Do not claim completion without fresh verification command evidence.
